msgid ""
"name: Bestow Curse\n"
"level: 3\n"
"school: necromancy\n"
"classes: bard\n"
"         cleric\n"
"         wizard\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bestow_curse.md:10
msgid "# Bestow Curse _3rd-level necromancy_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bestow_curse.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action   \n"
"**Range:** Touch   \n"
"**Components:** V, S   \n"
"**Duration:** Concentration, up to 1 minute \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bestow_curse.md:17
msgid ""
"You touch a creature, and that creature must succeed on a Wisdom saving "
"throw or become cursed for the duration of the spell. When you cast this "
"spell, choose the nature of the curse from the following options:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bestow_curse.md:22
msgid ""
"Choose one ability score. While cursed, the target has disadvantage on "
"ability checks and saving throws made with that ability score."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bestow_curse.md:22
msgid "While cursed, the target has disadvantage on attack rolls against you."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bestow_curse.md:22
msgid ""
"While cursed, the target must make a Wisdom saving throw at the start of "
"each of its turns. If it fails, it wastes its action that turn doing "
"nothing."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bestow_curse.md:22
msgid ""
"While the target is cursed, your attacks and spells deal an extra 1d8 "
"necrotic damage to the target."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bestow_curse.md:24
msgid ""
"A **_remove curse_** spell ends this effect. At the GM's option, you may "
"choose an alternative curse effect, but it should be no more powerful than "
"those described above. The GM has final say on such a curse's effect."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bestow_curse.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**At Higher Levels.** If you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level "
"or higher, the duration is concentration, up to 10 minutes. If you use a "
"spell slot of 5th level or higher, the duration is 8 hours. If you use a "
"spell slot of 7th level or higher, the duration is 24 hours. If you use a "
"9th level spell slot, the spell lasts until it is dispelled. Using a spell "
"slot of 5th level or higher grants a duration that doesn't require "
"concentration. \n"
msgstr ""
